d 'LMZTEST': module to test for Zipf´s law
d
d  This program calculates the test statistic for Zipf´s law 
d proposed by Urzúa (Econ.Lett., 2000). It is locally optimal if
d the possible alternative distributions are contained in the
d Pareto type (II) family. 
d
d KW: Zipf's law
d KW: Pareto distribution
d
d Requires: Stata version 14
d
d Distribution-Date: 20220602
d
d Author: Carlos M. Urzúa, Tecnológico de Monterrey
d Support: email curzua@@tec.mx
d
f lmztest.ado
f lmztest.sthlp
